'''冥卫五'''（{{lang-en|Styx}}，{{IPAc-en|'|s|t|ɪ|k|s}} ，编号'''S/2012 P 1'''、'''S/2012 (134340) 1'''，简称'''P5'''）是[[冥王星|冥王星]]的一颗较小的[[天然卫星|天然卫星]]，2012年7月11日宣布发现。它是冥王星第五颗被确认的卫星，距离第四颗卫星[[冥衛四|冥衛四]]的发现仅相隔了一年。2013年7月2日時，[[國際天文學聯合會|國際天文學聯合會]]宣布正式批准「[[斯堤克斯|斯堤克斯]]」（Styx）這個名字作為S/2012 (134340) 1的稱呼<ref>{{Cite web|title=Names for New Pluto Moons Accepted by the IAU After Public Vote|url=http://www.iau.org/public_press/news/detail/iau1303/|date=2013-07-02|publisher=[[國際天文學聯合會|IAU]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140323102528/http://www.iau.org/public_press/news/detail/iau1303/|archive-date=2014-03-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Pluto's Smallest Moons Receive Their Official Names|url=http://www.seti.org/seti-institute/press-release/plutos-smallest-moons-receive-their-official-names|date=2013-07-02|publisher=[[SETI协会|SETI]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130705222117/http://www.seti.org/seti-institute/press-release/plutos-smallest-moons-receive-their-official-names|archivedate=2013-07-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

==发现==
[[哈勃太空望远镜|哈勃太空望远镜]]上装有的[[第三代广域照相机|第三代广域照相机]]在2012年6月26日至7月9日间拍摄了九组照片，天文学家从这些照片发现了这颗卫星。<ref>{{Cite web|title=A cosmic discovery: Astronomers using NASA's Hubble Space Telescope find fifth moon orbiting Pluto|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2172229/Pluto-Astronomers-using-NASAs-Hubble-Space-Telescope-fifth-moon-orbiting-dwarf-planet.html|access-date=2021-12-06|date=2012-07-11|last=Preece|first=Rob|work=[[每日郵報|Mail Online]]|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206160953/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2172229/Pluto-Astronomers-using-NASAs-Hubble-Space-Telescope-fifth-moon-orbiting-dwarf-planet.html}}</ref>这些照片原本为[[新视野号|新视野号]]对冥王星的探测而准备，當時该飞船正在飞往冥王星，並預計在2015年7月14日飞过冥王星系统。人们不由得担忧，该区域可能隐藏着更多的难以观测到的小天体，高速穿越此区域的新视野号可能与这些未知小天体碰撞<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Hubble telescope spots fifth moon orbiting Pluto|url=https://www.csmonitor.com/Science/2012/0711/Hubble-telescope-spots-fifth-moon-orbiting-Pluto|date=2012-07-11|journal=Christian Science Monitor|issn=0882-7729|access-date=2021-12-06|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206163310/https://www.csmonitor.com/Science/2012/0711/Hubble-telescope-spots-fifth-moon-orbiting-Pluto}}</ref>。

==物理性质==
据估计，该卫星的上下边缘大约为0.04，[[反照率|反照率]]大约为0.35<ref name="Sanders">{{Cite web|title=Hubble Space Telescope detects fifth moon of Pluto (Update)|url=https://phys.org/news/2012-07-hubble-space-telescope-moon-pluto.html|access-date=2021-12-06|last=S|first=Ray|work=phys.org|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206142912/https://phys.org/news/2012-07-hubble-space-telescope-moon-pluto.html}}</ref>。再结合视星等，这颗卫星直径在10公里至25公里之间<ref>{{cite web|title=NewsCenter - Hubble Discovers a Fifth Moon Orbiting Pluto (07/11/2012) - The Full Story|url=http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/archive/releases/2012/32/full/|accessdate=2012-07-12|date=|publisher=HubbleSite|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120713215054/http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/archive/releases/2012/32/full/|archive-date=2012-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Hubble discovers new Pluto moon|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-18803212|newspaper=BBC News|date=2012-07-11|accessdate=2021-12-06|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206171001/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-18803212}}</ref>。

==轨道参数==
冥卫五的公转週期约为20.2天<ref name="Sanders" />，这说明它与[[冥卫一|冥卫一]]—冥王星体系处于大约5.4%的1:3[[轨道共振|共振]]。加上冥王星的[[冥王星的卫星|其他卫星]]——[[冥卫二|冥卫二]]、[[冥卫四|冥卫四]]和[[冥卫三|冥卫三]]，它们形成了部分1:3:4:5:6共振的近心点进动。

==起源==
据推测，环绕冥王星的复杂卫星系统是冥王星与另一个[[柯伊伯带天体|柯伊伯带天体]]在很久以前碰撞的结果<ref>{{Cite web|title=Astronomers find fifth moon at Pluto|url=https://www.latimes.com/science/la-xpm-2012-jul-11-sns-la-sci-sn-pluto-moon-20120711-story.html|access-date=2021-12-06|date=2012-07-11|work=Los Angeles Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206160959/https://www.latimes.com/science/la-xpm-2012-jul-11-sns-la-sci-sn-pluto-moon-20120711-story.html}}</ref>。冥王星的卫星可能是这样的相撞事件的[[碰撞家族|残骸所形成的]]，这与月球形成的[[大碰撞说|大碰撞说]]类似。轨道共振可能使残骸中聚集物质形成了卫星<ref name="Matson">{{Cite web|title=New Moon for Pluto: Hubble Telescope Spots a 5th Plutonian Satellite|url=https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/pluto-moon-p5/|access-date=2021-12-06|last=Matson|first=John|work=[[科学美国人|Scientific American]]|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408195748/https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/pluto-moon-p5/}}</ref>。

